# Mutating Arithmetic Unary Operators (should prob move to its dedicated lib)
[let ++ [fn [n]
    [
        mut n [+ n 1]
    ]
]]

[let -- [fn [n]
    [
        mut n [- n 1]
    ]
]]

[let ** [fn [n]
    [
        mut n [* n n]
    ]
]]

[let // [fn [n]
    [
        mut n [/ n 2]
    ]
]]